<review 
	  reviewerId="{{ reviewerId }}" 
	  {% if reviewerContextId %}reviewerContextId="{{ reviewerContextId }}" {% endif %}
	  reviewerName="{{ reviewerName }}" 
	  reviewerEmail="{{ reviewerEmail }}" 
	  reviewDate="{{ reviewDate }}" 
	  reviewedMajorRelease="{{ reviewedMajorRelease }}" 
	  reviewedMinorRelease="{{ reviewedMinorRelease }}" 
	  reviewedMajorRevision="{{ reviewedMajorRevision }}" 
	  reviewedMinorRevision="{{ reviewedMinorRevision }}"
	  >
	    {% if details %}
		<details>
        {{ details }}
		</details>
		{% endif %}
		{% if otherDetails %}
        <otherDetails>{{ otherDetails }}</otherDetails>
		{% endif %}
      </review>